 you don't require both pizzas, freeze the second portion of dough in a plastic freezer bag  after working dough into a ball in step 5. When you are ready to use the dough, remove from freezer, thaw dough to room temperature and then allow to pove for at least 15 minutes. You will need to make the garlic and rosemary mixture fresh on the day of serving."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","40m","8 portions"]}